Enum Securable

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Securable>
      • org.apache.derby.iapi.security.Securable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Securable>

    public enum Securable
extends java.lang.Enum<Securable>
    Operations which can be secured. SQL authorization is one way to control who can access these operations.
